WEBVTT

00:00.150 --> 00:02.283
Proper toothbrushing involves four things:...

00:03.005 --> 00:08.189
...a soft toothbrush, the correct angle of brushing and brushing in a pattern.

00:08.736 --> 00:10.945
It's important to brush at least twice a day:...

00:11.351 --> 00:15.099
...after breakfast and before bed using a soft toothbrush.

00:16.165 --> 00:20.725
A soft toothbrush also makes it much easier to remove the plaque below the gumline...

00:20.967 --> 00:22.799
...where periodontal disease starts.

00:23.717 --> 00:26.975
Use a pea-sized amount of toothpaste that contains fluoride.

00:27.367 --> 00:31.939
It might stop a cavity in its tracks and give you more resistance to future cavities.

